    (* ;; "Basically just adds an OPERATION argument to SHADEITEM.  Constructs a list of SHADE and OPERATION to be passed to SHADEITEM for its SHADE argument.  Corresponding advice to RESHADEITEM then uses OPERATION in shading ITEM.  Among other possibilities, this enables menus that have items of grayed text, which my be used to indicate that they are not available for the current operation. (Call with GRAYSHADE for SHADE and 'ERASE for OPERATION.)")

